ong \u2013 artwork, design\n* Andy C. Fellows \u2013 design\n\n==Charts==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\"| Chart (2016)\n! scope=\"col\"| Peak<br /> position\n|-\n{{albumchart|Australia|38|artist=In Flames|album=Battles|rowheader=true|accessdate=November 19, 2016}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|Austria|8|artist=In Flames|album=Battles|rowheader=true|accessdate=November 24, 2016}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|Flanders|45|artist=In Flames|album=Battles|rowheader=true|accessdate=November 19, 2016}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|Wallonia|58|artist=In Flames|album=Battles|rowheader=true|accessdate=November 19, 2016}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|BillboardCanada|19|artist=In Flames|rowheader=true|accessdate=November 22, 2016}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|Finland|3|artist=In Flames|album=Battles|rowheader=true|accessdate=November 20, 2016}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|France|101|artist=In Flames|album=Battles|rowheader=true|accessdate=November 22, 2016}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|Germany4|7|id=318094|artist=In Flames|album=Battles|rowheader=true|accessdate=November 19, 2016}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|Norway|13|artist=In Flames|album=Battles|rowheader=true|accessdate=November 19, 2016}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Spanish Albums ([[Productores de M\u00fasica de Espa\u00f1a|PROMUSICAE]])<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.promusicae.es/listas/semana/3283-%C3%81lbumes-semana-46-2016|title=TOP 100 ALBUMES \u2014 SEMANA 46: del 11.11.2016 al 17.11.2016|publisher=[[Productores de M\u00fasica de Espa\u00f1a]]|language=Spanish|accessdate=November 24, 2016}}</ref>\n| 83\n|-\n{{albumchart|Sweden|2|artist=In Flames|album=Battles|rowheader=true|accessdate=November 19, 2016}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|Switzerland|13|artist=In Flames|album=Battles|rowheader=true|accessdate=November 23, 2016}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|UK2|75|date=2016-11-18|rowheader=true|accessdate=November 19, 2016}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|Billboard200|60|artist=In Flames|rowheader=true|accessdate=November 22, 2016}}\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|2}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{Official website|http://www.inflames.com}}\n\n{{In Flames}}\n\n[[Category:2016 albums]]\n[[Category:In Flames albums]]\n[[Category:Nuclear Blast albums]]\n[[Category:Eleven Seven Label Group albums]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox album\n| name       = Battles\n| type       = studio\n| artist     = [[In Flames]]\n| cover      = File:In Flames Battles Album Cover.jpeg\n| alt        =\n| released   = {{Start date|2016|11|11}}\n| recorded   = February\u2013April 2016\n| venue      =\n| studio     = West Valley Studios, [[Woodland Hills, Los Angeles|Woodland Hills, California]], U.S.\n| genre      = [[Alternative metal]]<ref>{{cite web |last1=Weaver |first1=James |title=In the studio with In Flames as they work on their new album |url=https://www.loudersound.com/features/in-the-studio-with-in-flames-as-they-work-on-their-new-album |website=[[Metal Hammer]] |accessdate=7 September 2018}}</ref>\n| length     = 47:38\n| label      = [[Eleven Seven Music|Eleven Seven]], [[Nuclear Blast]]\n| producer   = [[Howard Benson]]\n| prev_title = [[Siren Charms]]\n| prev_year  = 2014\n| next_title = [[I, the Mask]]\n| next_year  = 2019\n| misc       = {{Singles\n | name        = Battles\n | type        = studio\n | single1     = The Truth\n | single1date = 26 August 2016\n | single2     = The End\n | single2date = 26 August 2016\n | single3     = Through My Eyes\n | single3date = 14 October 2016\n | single4     = Save Me\n | single4date = 4 November 2016\n | single5     = Here Until Forever\n | single5date = 12 May 2017\n}}\n}}\n{{Album ratings\n| rev1      = ''[[Loudwire]]''\n| rev1score = Positive<ref>{{cite magazine|magazine=[[Loudwire]]|last=Bowar|first=Chad|url=http://loudwire.com/in-flames-battles-album-review/|title=In Flames, 'Battles'|date=November 11, 2016|accessdate=December 18, 2016}}</ref>\n| rev2      = ''[[Metal Hammer]]''\n| rev2score = {{rating|3.5|5}}<ref name=\"Metal Hammer\">{{cite magazine|magazine=[[Metal Hammer]]|last=Barbour|first=Rob|url=http://t