 on Yemen|url=https://www.huffingtonpost.com/samuel-ramani/why-putin-is-keeping-a-cl_b_12184874.html|website=www.huffingtonpost.com|publisher=The Huffington Post|accessdate=30 March 2017|date=4 October 2016}}\n*{{cite web|last1=Almasmari|first1=Hakim|last2=Fitch|first2=Asa|title=Yemen\u2019s Houthis Seek Iran, Russia and China Ties|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/yemens-houthis-seek-iran-russia-and-china-ties-1425664867|website=www.wsj.com|publisher=The Wall Street Journal|accessdate=30 March 2017|date=6 March 2015}}</ref> -->\n\n<ref name=Hezbollah>See:\n*{{cite web|last1=Al-Abyad|first1=Said|title=Yemeni Officer: 4 Lebanese 'Hezbollah' Members Caught in Ma'rib|url=http://english.aawsat.com/s-alabyad/news-middle-east/yemeni-officer-4-lebanese-hezbollah-members-caught-marib|website=english.aawsat.com|publisher=Asharq Al-Awsat|accessdate=30 March 2017|date=11 March 2017|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170321042628/http://english.aawsat.com/s-alabyad/news-middle-east/yemeni-officer-4-lebanese-hezbollah-members-caught-marib|archivedate=21 March 2017}}\n*{{cite web|last1=Pestano|first1=Andrew V.|title=Yemen accuses Hezbollah of supporting Houthi attacks in Saudi Arabia|url=http://www.upi.com/Top_News/World-News/2016/02/25/Yemen-accuses-Hezbollah-of-supporting-Houthi-attacks-in-Saudi-Arabia/4971456399472/|website=www.upi.com|publisher=United Press International|date=25 February 2016|location=Sana'a, Yemen|accessdate=30 March 2017|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170317143211/http://www.upi.com/Top_News/World-News/2016/02/25/Yemen-accuses-Hezbollah-of-supporting-Houthi-attacks-in-Saudi-Arabia/4971456399472/|archivedate=17 March 2017}}\n*{{cite web|last1=Hatem|first1=Mohammed|title=Yemen Accuses Hezbollah of Helping Houthis in Saudi Border War|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2016-02-24/yemen-accuses-hezbollah-of-helping-houthis-in-saudi-border-war|website=www.bloomberg.com|publisher=Bloomberg News|accessdate=30 